1
00:01:31,380 --> 00:01:34,900
=Generation to Generation=

2
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:37,940
=Episode 7=

3
00:01:49,410 --> 00:01:50,620
You haven't rested well lately.

4
00:01:51,410 --> 00:01:52,250
Today,

5
00:01:52,660 --> 00:01:53,740
you should rest easy.

6
00:01:56,570 --> 00:01:58,460
You usually do housework?

7
00:01:59,930 --> 00:02:02,260
Just some small chores.

8
00:02:03,490 --> 00:02:05,460
I thought the Young Master
of the demon sect

9
00:02:06,210 --> 00:02:07,850
lived in luxury,

10
00:02:07,930 --> 00:02:08,890
with servants

11
00:02:09,340 --> 00:02:10,660
at his beck and call.

12
00:02:10,940 --> 00:02:11,993
You read it in a storybook?

13
00:02:13,730 --> 00:02:14,820
Father doesn't like noise.

14
00:02:16,410 --> 00:02:17,690
He told me

15
00:02:18,260 --> 00:02:19,660
that cleaning every inch

16
00:02:20,010 --> 00:02:21,380
of his room

17
00:02:21,850 --> 00:02:22,890
and organizing every book

18
00:02:23,060 --> 00:02:24,100
he's read

19
00:02:24,730 --> 00:02:25,570
was immensely joyful.

20
00:02:25,980 --> 00:02:26,820
Your father is

21
00:02:28,220 --> 00:02:30,220
not quite the man

22
00:02:30,220 --> 00:02:31,060
I imagined.

23
00:02:33,410 --> 00:02:35,170
In the stories,

24
00:02:36,220 --> 00:02:37,060
all the Mus

25
00:02:37,290 --> 00:02:38,820
are bloodthirsty villains.

26
00:02:45,010 --> 00:02:45,850
Where's Qian Xueshen?

27
00:02:46,190 --> 00:02:47,030
Don't worry.

28
00:02:47,060 --> 00:02:48,400
He has a whole group serving him.

29
00:02:48,980 --> 00:02:50,130
Right now,

30
00:02:50,380 --> 00:02:51,540
it should be quite lively.

31
00:02:56,850 --> 00:02:57,690
We're both guests.

32
00:02:57,940 --> 00:02:59,260
Why is the treatment so different?

33
00:03:03,780 --> 00:03:04,620
Mu,

34
00:03:05,100 --> 00:03:06,540
how can you treat me like this?

35
00:03:08,890 --> 00:03:09,983
The journey through the snow

36
00:03:10,096 --> 00:03:11,820
is not as simple
as walking down the street

37
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:13,260
to buy a box of rouge.

38
00:03:14,940 --> 00:03:15,940
This lawless land

39
00:03:16,610 --> 00:03:17,450
has fierce customs.

40
00:03:18,010 --> 00:03:18,850
It's very dangerous.

41
00:03:19,170 --> 00:03:20,940
One misstep could lead to a trap.

42
00:03:21,220 --> 00:03:22,380
This place is so dangerous.

43
00:03:22,730 --> 00:03:23,570
I think

44
00:03:24,450 --> 00:03:25,540
I should go with you.

45
00:03:25,940 --> 00:03:26,780
Lately,

46
00:03:27,260 --> 00:03:29,730
you've risked enough for me.

47
00:03:30,540 --> 00:03:31,380
Besides,

48
00:03:31,610 --> 00:03:33,850
isn't Nie Zhe clearing out
the Mu remnants?

49
00:03:34,130 --> 00:03:35,340
You'd better stay out of sight.

50
00:03:37,850 --> 00:03:38,890
Zhao, are you worried

51
00:03:39,890 --> 00:03:40,730
about me?

52
00:03:42,220 --> 00:03:44,100
I just think Nie Zhe is detestable.

53
00:03:46,290 --> 00:03:47,130
By the way,

54
00:03:51,060 --> 00:03:52,540
why did your Li Sect end up

55
00:03:52,780 --> 00:03:54,410
with the Nie clan?

56
00:03:56,340 --> 00:03:58,380
My great-grandfather
adopted Nie Hengcheng.

57
00:03:58,946 --> 00:04:00,260
He later assisted my grandfather.

58
00:04:00,570 --> 00:04:01,493
Grandfather died young.

59
00:04:01,820 --> 00:04:03,660
At that time, Father was not yet ten,

60
00:04:04,220 --> 00:04:06,130
so Nie Hengcheng took over the sect

61
00:04:06,620 --> 00:04:07,610
until Father came of age.

62
00:04:08,380 --> 00:04:10,130
But Father had no interest in power,

63
00:04:10,690 --> 00:04:12,540
so Nie Hengcheng kept running the sect,

64
00:04:13,170 --> 00:04:15,340
eventually taking it as his own.

65
00:04:16,290 --> 00:04:18,370
What kind of person is Nie Hengcheng

66
00:04:19,340 --> 00:04:20,290
that my aunt

67
00:04:21,050 --> 00:04:22,460
would risk her life to kill him?

68
00:04:23,100 --> 00:04:24,290
Nie Hengcheng is talented

69
00:04:24,460 --> 00:04:25,379
and rare in the world.

70
00:04:26,170 --> 00:04:27,610
To the Six Sects,

71
00:04:27,660 --> 00:04:28,810
he's a demon.

72
00:04:29,580 --> 00:04:30,460
But in our sect,

73
00:04:31,340 --> 00:04:32,730
he is a pillar of the world,

74
00:04:33,580 --> 00:04:34,490
an unshakable anchor.

75
00:04:36,540 --> 00:04:37,460
Then why did he

76
00:04:37,700 --> 00:04:38,930
go against all rules,

77
00:04:39,020 --> 00:04:40,046
killing without restraint?

78
00:04:40,540 --> 00:04:41,780
That's because later

79
00:04:41,850 --> 00:04:43,540
he mastered a supreme skill

80
00:04:46,540 --> 00:04:48,250
that was called the Ziwei Method

81
00:04:48,460 --> 00:04:49,930
and was created by the Mu ancestors.

82
00:04:50,460 --> 00:04:51,700
This method

83
00:04:51,780 --> 00:04:52,730
was powerful

84
00:04:52,730 --> 00:04:53,780
and invincible,

85
00:04:54,490 --> 00:04:55,700
but long lost.

86
00:04:55,810 --> 00:04:57,259
Later, Nie Hengcheng somehow acquired

87
00:04:57,270 --> 00:04:58,490
its cultivation method,

88
00:04:58,700 --> 00:05:00,540
and it became the root of all disasters.

89
00:05:00,610 --> 00:05:02,250
Father told me about this skill.

90
00:05:02,660 --> 00:05:04,020
He said such a defiant skill

91
00:05:04,340 --> 00:05:05,410
must have hidden dangers;

92
00:05:05,619 --> 00:05:06,799
better not to practice at all.

93
00:05:08,850 --> 00:05:10,580
Your father is
truly a man of detachment.

94
00:05:11,460 --> 00:05:12,300
I've always wondered:

95
00:05:13,540 --> 00:05:14,930
If Father weren't so detached

96
00:05:16,100 --> 00:05:18,220
and hadn't handed over
the Chief position,

97
00:05:18,730 --> 00:05:20,310
how many lives

98
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:21,340
would have changed?

99
00:05:22,580 --> 00:05:24,460
Wu Yuanying wouldn't have suffered

100
00:05:24,460 --> 00:05:25,580
for ten years.

101
00:05:27,050 --> 00:05:28,100
Ms. Cai Pingshu

102
00:05:28,700 --> 00:05:29,850
wouldn't have died so early.

103
00:05:31,250 --> 00:05:32,410
It's not his fault.

104
00:05:34,900 --> 00:05:36,810
He simply didn't want to go
against his heart.

105
00:05:37,490 --> 00:05:38,540
My aunt was like that, too.

106
00:05:39,980 --> 00:05:41,250
She was bold and fearless

107
00:05:42,460 --> 00:05:45,410
but afraid of being trapped at home.

108
00:05:46,540 --> 00:05:47,930
Perhaps the same applies

109
00:05:48,540 --> 00:05:49,380
to your father.

110
00:05:50,540 --> 00:05:51,380
Your father

111
00:05:51,700 --> 00:05:53,050
must be a very good man.

112
00:05:53,850 --> 00:05:54,780
Otherwise, Uncle Chang

113
00:05:54,780 --> 00:05:57,206
wouldn't trust you so easily
after a single act of kindness.

114
00:05:57,930 --> 00:05:59,276
It must be because of your father

115
00:05:59,660 --> 00:06:00,810
that he believes

116
00:06:01,810 --> 00:06:02,776
you're not a bad person.

117
00:06:04,980 --> 00:06:05,820
Zhao...

118
00:06:12,250 --> 00:06:13,090
What's wrong?

119
00:06:35,220 --> 00:06:36,060
Thank you.

120
00:06:56,660 --> 00:06:58,133
(Uncle Cheng, Li Sect)
Young Master,

121
00:06:58,144 --> 00:06:59,889
you weren't affected
by the sleeping powder,

122
00:06:59,900 --> 00:07:02,050
so why let Miss Cai go?

123
00:07:06,370 --> 00:07:07,580
To cheer her up.

124
00:07:45,660 --> 00:07:46,610
What a worthless bird.

125
00:07:47,020 --> 00:07:48,266
It probably follows its master.

126
00:07:50,780 --> 00:07:52,100
It's about to snow.

127
00:07:52,780 --> 00:07:53,900
This place is so remote.

128
00:07:54,780 --> 00:07:56,250
Is there somewhere to stay?

129
00:08:40,770 --> 00:08:41,610
Ma'am,

130
00:08:41,650 --> 00:08:42,700
we're here to stay.

131
00:08:45,060 --> 00:08:46,130
Miss,

132
00:08:46,770 --> 00:08:47,700
may I ask your name?

133
00:08:49,650 --> 00:08:50,490
I'm Feng Xiaohan.

134
00:08:50,770 --> 00:08:52,100
This is my...

135
00:08:52,610 --> 00:08:53,450
Well.

136
00:08:53,650 --> 00:08:54,980
My fiancé,

137
00:08:55,650 --> 00:08:56,490
Wan Dazhuang.

138
00:08:56,650 --> 00:08:57,490
Wan...

139
00:08:59,300 --> 00:09:00,580
Since you two are a couple,

140
00:09:03,580 --> 00:09:04,580
Blooming Flowers

141
00:09:04,770 --> 00:09:06,340
is our best room.

142
00:09:06,610 --> 00:09:07,850
It has a soft animal-skin bed

143
00:09:07,850 --> 00:09:08,700
and fine bedding,

144
00:09:09,130 --> 00:09:10,670
and the back door leads to hot springs.

145
00:09:10,850 --> 00:09:11,730
Very romantic.

146
00:09:12,420 --> 00:09:13,420
Payment

147
00:09:14,300 --> 00:09:15,180
can be settled later

148
00:09:15,580 --> 00:09:17,220
at checkout.

149
00:09:18,610 --> 00:09:20,300
I didn't expect such attentive service

150
00:09:20,530 --> 00:09:22,340
(Blooming Flowers)
in this harsh, cold land.

151
00:09:22,490 --> 00:09:24,060
Right, Dazhuang?

152
00:09:27,530 --> 00:09:29,010
I'll bring your meal first.

153
00:09:30,530 --> 00:09:32,060
You two look young

154
00:09:32,370 --> 00:09:33,300
and delicate.

155
00:09:33,650 --> 00:09:35,340
Why come to this freezing place?

156
00:09:38,460 --> 00:09:40,250
To see the snowy scenery.

157
00:09:40,580 --> 00:09:41,420
See the scenery?

158
00:09:41,980 --> 00:09:43,420
This blizzard

159
00:09:44,010 --> 00:09:45,890
is hardly a good time to sightsee.

160
00:09:45,980 --> 00:09:46,820
Is that so?

161
00:09:49,890 --> 00:09:51,580
I'll set the dishes for you.

162
00:09:52,850 --> 00:09:53,770
Thanks, ma'am.

163
00:09:56,060 --> 00:09:57,530
It's too hot!

164
00:09:59,890 --> 00:10:00,730
Sorry.

165
00:10:00,730 --> 00:10:01,570
I'm sorry.

166
00:10:01,890 --> 00:10:02,770
Sorry to disturb you.

167
00:10:03,370 --> 00:10:04,220
Sorry.

168
00:10:04,250 --> 00:10:05,090
I'm sorry.

169
00:10:06,490 --> 00:10:07,330
Sorry.

170
00:10:07,580 --> 00:10:08,460
Sorry to disturb you.

171
00:10:08,890 --> 00:10:10,220
I'm too clumsy.

172
00:10:12,370 --> 00:10:14,100
(Qinong)
Are you also here for the saliva?

173
00:10:15,130 --> 00:10:16,100
What saliva?

174
00:10:16,850 --> 00:10:18,940
The saliva of the Snow-Scale Beast.

175
00:10:19,420 --> 00:10:21,730
It's said the long-lost Snow-Scale Beast

176
00:10:21,730 --> 00:10:23,060
is about to appear.

177
00:10:23,610 --> 00:10:25,610
Its saliva can repair internal energy

178
00:10:25,610 --> 00:10:26,530
and grant longevity.

179
00:10:26,940 --> 00:10:28,180
My master is weak,

180
00:10:28,650 --> 00:10:30,370
so we're hoping for some luck.

181
00:10:30,700 --> 00:10:31,980
Qinong.

182
00:10:32,610 --> 00:10:33,730
I need to go back.

183
00:10:44,770 --> 00:10:45,610
Slow down.

184
00:10:45,820 --> 00:10:46,660
Wan Dazhuang?

185
00:10:48,370 --> 00:10:49,460
Eyes frozen

186
00:10:49,460 --> 00:10:50,340
on the beauty?

187
00:11:03,340 --> 00:11:04,250
Miss,

188
00:11:05,100 --> 00:11:06,610
this place isn't safe.

189
00:11:07,100 --> 00:11:08,490
Do you want us

190
00:11:08,730 --> 00:11:09,850
to scout the path?

191
00:11:10,220 --> 00:11:11,180
Go away!

192
00:11:39,530 --> 00:11:40,370
You...

193
00:11:41,460 --> 00:11:42,300
It wasn't me.

194
00:11:45,060 --> 00:11:45,900
It was me.

195
00:12:16,060 --> 00:12:17,530
I've looked for you for so long.

196
00:12:23,610 --> 00:12:24,850
Why betray me

197
00:12:25,010 --> 00:12:26,250
and elope with this pretty boy?

198
00:12:29,580 --> 00:12:30,460
Sir,

199
00:12:30,940 --> 00:12:32,610
your attack is so cruel.

200
00:12:33,100 --> 00:12:34,980
Though their behavior was wrong,

201
00:12:35,180 --> 00:12:36,340
they didn't deserve death.

202
00:12:38,820 --> 00:12:39,660
You...

203
00:12:45,890 --> 00:12:46,730
Everyone,

204
00:12:48,850 --> 00:12:51,850
those two are notorious rapists
in the northwest,

205
00:12:52,180 --> 00:12:54,193
killing dozens of women.

206
00:12:54,204 --> 00:12:55,369
(Zhou Zhiqin, Peiqiong Manor)

207
00:12:55,380 --> 00:12:56,490
They deserved

208
00:12:57,220 --> 00:12:58,580
such deaths.

209
00:12:59,700 --> 00:13:01,770
This is Uncle Zhou's cousin.

210
00:13:02,220 --> 00:13:03,490
I saw him as a child.

211
00:13:05,490 --> 00:13:07,460
Are you from Peiqiong Manor?

212
00:13:08,460 --> 00:13:09,850
I'm Zhou Zhiqin.

213
00:13:11,220 --> 00:13:12,300
May I ask

214
00:13:13,010 --> 00:13:14,100
your name?

215
00:13:14,530 --> 00:13:15,420
I am

216
00:13:17,100 --> 00:13:17,940
Yan Ning.

217
00:13:18,980 --> 00:13:20,610
Thanks for your help, Mr. Zhou.

218
00:13:25,580 --> 00:13:26,980
You're my fiancée,

219
00:13:27,940 --> 00:13:29,490
yet you ran off with my heirloom

220
00:13:29,940 --> 00:13:31,820
and this pretty boy.

221
00:13:32,180 --> 00:13:33,220
Surely, I'd look for you.

222
00:13:34,060 --> 00:13:35,370
Who took your heirloom?

223
00:13:35,370 --> 00:13:37,180
Wait. Who is your fiancée?

224
00:13:37,250 --> 00:13:39,010
I'm not the pretty boy either.

225
00:13:40,580 --> 00:13:42,250
Isn't this my heirloom,

226
00:13:42,250 --> 00:13:43,940
the scale of the Snow-Scale Beast?

227
00:13:47,820 --> 00:13:48,700
What a pity.

228
00:13:49,010 --> 00:13:50,890
The pretty boy defiled it.

229
00:13:53,580 --> 00:13:54,546
I don't want it anymore.

230
00:13:58,690 --> 00:13:59,540
I want it.

231
00:14:00,050 --> 00:14:00,910
Give it to me!

232
00:14:01,130 --> 00:14:02,190
Mine!

233
00:14:02,610 --> 00:14:03,550
Mine!

234
00:14:05,980 --> 00:14:06,850
Played enough?

235
00:14:08,850 --> 00:14:10,250
Just some Jianghu punks.

236
00:14:11,060 --> 00:14:12,730
They can hardly fight.

237
00:14:13,100 --> 00:14:14,250
Except for Mr. Zhou,

238
00:14:14,700 --> 00:14:15,700
they're nothing.

239
00:14:17,010 --> 00:14:19,530
Those three haven't acted yet.

240
00:14:28,490 --> 00:14:30,820
Why did your Uncle Zhou
also want the scale?

241
00:14:31,530 --> 00:14:32,580
I don't know.

242
00:14:33,180 --> 00:14:34,370
This is enough.

243
00:14:41,890 --> 00:14:43,340
No wonder it's a family heirloom.

244
00:14:43,370 --> 00:14:45,730
I heard the Snow-Scale Beast
can sense this scale.

245
00:14:46,650 --> 00:14:47,700
Losing it would be a shame.

246
00:14:49,300 --> 00:14:50,340
Why not lend it to me?

247
00:14:51,530 --> 00:14:53,980
Dazhuang has been weak since childhood.

248
00:14:54,340 --> 00:14:55,759
I want to secure the saliva for him.

249
00:14:57,010 --> 00:14:58,890
So, it is for the pretty boy.

250
00:15:04,980 --> 00:15:05,820
Mr. Yan,

251
00:15:06,370 --> 00:15:08,180
my son had an accident here last year.

252
00:15:09,530 --> 00:15:10,850
The guards who escaped said

253
00:15:11,610 --> 00:15:13,420
he encountered the Snow-Scale Beast

254
00:15:13,700 --> 00:15:14,540
and died.

255
00:15:15,460 --> 00:15:17,180
I just want to retrieve his body

256
00:15:17,420 --> 00:15:18,420
for a proper burial.

257
00:15:19,490 --> 00:15:20,700
Please, Mr. Yan,

258
00:15:21,340 --> 00:15:22,250
lend me the scale.

259
00:15:23,300 --> 00:15:24,190
Give it to me.

260
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:25,690
- Give it to me.
- Mr. Yan.

261
00:15:25,850 --> 00:15:26,690
Give it to me.

262
00:15:27,373 --> 00:15:28,748
- Give it to me.
- I need it, too.

263
00:15:28,759 --> 00:15:29,540
Mr. Yan.

264
00:15:30,700 --> 00:15:31,540
Good.

265
00:15:31,980 --> 00:15:33,130
Once we find the saliva,

266
00:15:33,730 --> 00:15:35,250
you'll come back with me.

267
00:15:37,010 --> 00:15:38,010
Tomorrow morning,

268
00:15:38,340 --> 00:15:39,650
let's set off

269
00:15:40,460 --> 00:15:41,820
to find the saliva.

270
00:15:42,180 --> 00:15:43,220
Okay.

271
00:15:47,940 --> 00:15:50,300
Where did you get the scale?

272
00:15:51,300 --> 00:15:52,220
The Jiuzhou Archive.

273
00:15:54,180 --> 00:15:55,220
Does it have slime?

274
00:15:55,420 --> 00:15:56,580
That kind of substance

275
00:15:56,850 --> 00:15:57,956
does not congeal in the cold

276
00:15:58,060 --> 00:15:58,980
and melts when heated.

277
00:15:59,820 --> 00:16:01,460
The archive
hasn't been cleaned for ages.

278
00:16:01,650 --> 00:16:02,843
So, it couldn't be preserved.

279
00:16:03,676 --> 00:16:05,089
Are we really going up the mountain

280
00:16:05,100 --> 00:16:06,370
with those people tomorrow?

281
00:16:06,700 --> 00:16:07,973
The enemy is better in the open

282
00:16:08,180 --> 00:16:09,180
than in the dark.

283
00:16:11,940 --> 00:16:13,490
Why did you chase after us?

284
00:16:16,130 --> 00:16:17,940
You stole my Peng.

285
00:16:18,723 --> 00:16:20,010
Of course, I had to get it back.

286
00:16:24,730 --> 00:16:25,570
Sleeping powder?

287
00:16:48,100 --> 00:16:49,010
The landlady?

288
00:16:50,130 --> 00:16:51,650
Why sneak in

289
00:16:52,060 --> 00:16:53,060
at night?

290
00:16:54,300 --> 00:16:55,560
The snow mountains have spirits.

291
00:16:55,940 --> 00:16:57,370
Trespassers won't fare well.

292
00:16:57,820 --> 00:16:58,700
I advise you two

293
00:16:58,850 --> 00:16:59,890
to return the way you came

294
00:17:00,530 --> 00:17:02,100
to save your lives.

295
00:17:03,300 --> 00:17:04,373
You must be very familiar

296
00:17:04,620 --> 00:17:06,290
with the snowy mountains.

297
00:17:06,900 --> 00:17:07,740
Better stay

298
00:17:08,180 --> 00:17:09,140
and guide us.

299
00:17:19,420 --> 00:17:20,700
Hidden elites.

300
00:17:21,620 --> 00:17:22,460
Interesting.

301
00:17:52,250 --> 00:17:53,220
You're still sick.

302
00:17:53,860 --> 00:17:54,730
Why come here?

303
00:17:58,940 --> 00:18:00,366
Are you worried about that Cai girl?

304
00:18:01,232 --> 00:18:02,702
If not for fearing I'd slow her down,

305
00:18:03,530 --> 00:18:04,620
I would go with her.

306
00:18:06,570 --> 00:18:08,810
Zhao is not simple.

307
00:18:09,530 --> 00:18:11,900
She might bring back the antidote.

308
00:18:12,220 --> 00:18:13,060
Yuzhi,

309
00:18:13,620 --> 00:18:16,490
you've never seemed to care
so much about Lingbo.

310
00:18:18,860 --> 00:18:19,810
Master is in danger;

311
00:18:20,290 --> 00:18:21,530
the sect is in peril.

312
00:18:22,050 --> 00:18:23,460
Yet you still have time for jokes?

313
00:18:25,380 --> 00:18:26,290
Don't worry.

314
00:18:26,660 --> 00:18:27,500
With me here,

315
00:18:28,420 --> 00:18:30,530
Qingque Sect won't fall into chaos.

316
00:19:44,530 --> 00:19:45,940
I'm still here.

317
00:20:10,220 --> 00:20:11,420
There's not even a direction.

318
00:20:11,900 --> 00:20:13,090
Where do we start looking?

319
00:20:13,570 --> 00:20:14,460
Elder Tianji,

320
00:20:16,180 --> 00:20:17,330
let's find a place to rest.

321
00:20:17,730 --> 00:20:18,570
Alright.

322
00:20:19,220 --> 00:20:21,290
Everyone, rest up ahead.

323
00:20:21,700 --> 00:20:22,540
Let's go.

324
00:20:30,530 --> 00:20:31,370
Qian Xueshen,

325
00:20:31,700 --> 00:20:33,050
why so quiet today?

326
00:20:33,490 --> 00:20:35,010
That's unusual.

327
00:20:38,900 --> 00:20:40,140
Where's Mr. Zhang trailing us?

328
00:20:40,530 --> 00:20:41,460
Who saw him?

329
00:20:48,700 --> 00:20:49,540
Something's wrong.

330
00:20:50,490 --> 00:20:51,570
We just came this way.

331
00:20:51,900 --> 00:20:53,090
I've seen this stone.

332
00:20:53,530 --> 00:20:54,730
We're back here again.

333
00:20:56,570 --> 00:20:57,460
A ghost maze?

334
00:21:00,940 --> 00:21:02,140
What a mess.

335
00:21:02,220 --> 00:21:03,220
When we first came here,

336
00:21:03,420 --> 00:21:04,260
we went straight...

337
00:21:07,660 --> 00:21:08,500
It's a maze.

338
00:21:08,730 --> 00:21:09,930
Everyone, line up,

339
00:21:10,010 --> 00:21:10,850
one after another.

340
00:21:11,250 --> 00:21:12,220
Try not to get separated.

341
00:21:12,700 --> 00:21:13,860
This...

342
00:21:13,860 --> 00:21:14,710
It's getting dark.

343
00:21:14,720 --> 00:21:16,420
With a ghost maze, we'll never get out.

344
00:21:17,380 --> 00:21:18,700
We'll either freeze

345
00:21:18,700 --> 00:21:19,810
or starve to death here.

346
00:21:31,280 --> 00:21:32,719
Where there's a will, there's a way.

347
00:21:32,730 --> 00:21:33,730
As long as we follow it,

348
00:21:33,770 --> 00:21:34,900
we can escape the maze.

349
00:21:35,090 --> 00:21:35,930
Move.

350
00:21:37,220 --> 00:21:38,060
Come on.

351
00:21:45,530 --> 00:21:47,010
Unordinary fingers.

352
00:21:47,290 --> 00:21:48,140
He knows palm kills

353
00:21:51,140 --> 00:21:52,900
and can break the ice with inner power

354
00:21:53,290 --> 00:21:54,250
to break the maze.

355
00:21:55,420 --> 00:21:56,700
Who is he?

356
00:22:03,380 --> 00:22:04,220
There's a house.

357
00:22:04,710 --> 00:22:06,239
Everyone, get inside to avoid the snow.

358
00:22:06,250 --> 00:22:07,090
Let's go.

359
00:22:16,380 --> 00:22:17,220
Hurry.

360
00:22:17,420 --> 00:22:18,260
Come on.

361
00:22:20,050 --> 00:22:20,890
Follow closely.

362
00:22:39,250 --> 00:22:40,940
This place has been abandoned for years.

363
00:22:53,900 --> 00:22:54,900
Shu?

364
00:23:00,810 --> 00:23:01,770
You two,

365
00:23:02,220 --> 00:23:03,940
find a place to sleep.

366
00:23:45,010 --> 00:23:46,380
Time to eat.

367
00:23:48,900 --> 00:23:50,620
He's truly exhausted.

368
00:24:01,220 --> 00:24:02,180
He won't get cold.

369
00:24:10,220 --> 00:24:11,330
This trip

370
00:24:11,900 --> 00:24:13,220
is undoubtedly perilous.

371
00:24:14,140 --> 00:24:15,660
Are you really going to accompany me?

372
00:24:19,250 --> 00:24:20,660
Though you're heartless toward me,

373
00:24:22,490 --> 00:24:23,900
I can't do the same to you.

374
00:24:38,660 --> 00:24:39,810
That old servant

375
00:24:41,140 --> 00:24:42,620
reminds me of someone.

376
00:24:45,620 --> 00:24:46,460
Who?

377
00:24:46,810 --> 00:24:48,596
Another adopted son
of my great-grandfather,

378
00:24:49,330 --> 00:24:50,380
Elder Tianji,

379
00:24:50,770 --> 00:24:51,610
Duan Jiuxiu.

380
00:24:53,980 --> 00:24:55,530
He and Nie Hengcheng were both adopted.

381
00:24:56,290 --> 00:24:57,980
Why was Nie Hengcheng the Chief,

382
00:24:58,700 --> 00:24:59,813
while he was just an elder?

383
00:25:01,290 --> 00:25:02,460
So, he couldn't accept it.

384
00:25:04,050 --> 00:25:06,250
16 years ago,
the Lord of Qingfeng Temple

385
00:25:06,420 --> 00:25:07,980
mocked him as the eternal second.

386
00:25:08,420 --> 00:25:10,140
He slaughtered the entire temple

387
00:25:11,050 --> 00:25:12,660
and even turned young novices under ten

388
00:25:13,380 --> 00:25:14,620
into human fodder.

389
00:25:19,980 --> 00:25:22,420
Later, your aunt issued a Death Warrant.

390
00:25:22,960 --> 00:25:23,810
It's said

391
00:25:23,810 --> 00:25:25,620
he died in a ruined temple.

392
00:25:40,940 --> 00:25:42,660
The footprint of the Snow-Scale Beast.

393
00:25:45,940 --> 00:25:46,900
Congratulations, Master.

394
00:25:46,900 --> 00:25:48,100
Move, move!

395
00:25:49,180 --> 00:25:50,020
Let's go!

396
00:26:03,570 --> 00:26:05,250
It's the Jade Statue.

397
00:26:07,220 --> 00:26:08,810
The flowers on the base look

398
00:26:09,250 --> 00:26:11,730
like the tri-colored peach blossoms
unique to Luoying Valley.

399
00:26:13,220 --> 00:26:14,620
Could she be Gu Qingkong?

400
00:26:14,980 --> 00:26:15,900
In the wilderness,

401
00:26:16,220 --> 00:26:17,810
who put this statue here?

402
00:27:01,770 --> 00:27:02,730
All dead.

403
00:27:07,380 --> 00:27:08,490
Dead for over six months.

404
00:27:14,660 --> 00:27:15,500
There's a hole here.

405
00:27:15,880 --> 00:27:16,720
A hole?

406
00:27:34,090 --> 00:27:34,930
Wait.

407
00:27:37,570 --> 00:27:38,610
There's something inside.

408
00:27:49,940 --> 00:27:50,810
A snake!

409
00:27:50,810 --> 00:27:52,050
A huge snake!

410
00:28:01,810 --> 00:28:03,180
Qian Xueshen!

411
00:28:26,570 --> 00:28:27,700
The Red-Eyed Crystal Python,

412
00:28:27,900 --> 00:28:28,740
an ancient beast.

413
00:28:29,036 --> 00:28:30,632
Its breath can connect to the underworld

414
00:28:30,643 --> 00:28:31,530
and freeze everything.

415
00:28:31,700 --> 00:28:32,550
Zhao,

416
00:28:32,570 --> 00:28:33,410
stay close to me.

417
00:28:33,940 --> 00:28:34,780
Alright.

418
00:28:39,250 --> 00:28:40,090
Run!

419
00:28:45,380 --> 00:28:46,220
Qian Xueshen!

420
00:29:18,180 --> 00:29:19,020
Go!

421
00:29:46,456 --> 00:29:47,460
I thought you'd care less

422
00:29:47,460 --> 00:29:48,730
about life and death

423
00:29:49,250 --> 00:29:51,620
after the Qingque Sect massacre.

424
00:29:52,940 --> 00:29:54,700
Qian Xueshen came with me.

425
00:29:56,420 --> 00:29:57,530
He's not evil.

426
00:29:58,090 --> 00:29:59,330
If he falls into the hands

427
00:29:59,330 --> 00:30:00,220
of the Demonic Camp,

428
00:30:00,490 --> 00:30:01,460
after they use him,

429
00:30:02,180 --> 00:30:03,140
he'll be dead anyway.

430
00:30:04,810 --> 00:30:05,980
Jianghu is like this.

431
00:30:07,290 --> 00:30:08,980
Only ruthlessness ensures survival.

432
00:30:10,180 --> 00:30:11,290
If you're not ruthless,

433
00:30:12,810 --> 00:30:14,700
you'll end up like Qian Xueshen.

434
00:30:16,420 --> 00:30:17,260
Yulin,

435
00:30:18,460 --> 00:30:19,380
I'm here.

436
00:30:20,380 --> 00:30:22,050
I'll take you home.

437
00:30:34,460 --> 00:30:36,290
That's Zhou Zhiqin's son, Zhou Yulin.

438
00:30:42,330 --> 00:30:43,170
Yulin...

439
00:30:43,290 --> 00:30:45,330
- Mr. Zhou found his son.
- Yulin.

440
00:30:52,860 --> 00:30:53,700
That is...

441
00:30:54,420 --> 00:30:56,940
(Mr. Zhou wants the saliva for himself.)

442
00:30:58,050 --> 00:30:58,890
Jiu,

443
00:30:59,860 --> 00:31:01,460
go help Mr. Zhou.

444
00:31:01,460 --> 00:31:02,300
Yes.

445
00:31:11,460 --> 00:31:12,300
Don't come near.

446
00:31:13,330 --> 00:31:14,380
I don't need your help.

447
00:31:15,180 --> 00:31:16,490
I'll take Yulin back myself.

448
00:31:17,770 --> 00:31:20,530
Better let me help you.

449
00:31:52,490 --> 00:31:54,140
Is this the Snow-Scale Beast's saliva?

450
00:31:54,860 --> 00:31:56,090
Return it.

451
00:32:10,050 --> 00:32:10,890
Mr. Zhou.

452
00:32:12,420 --> 00:32:13,260
Mr. Zhou.

453
00:32:14,220 --> 00:32:15,530
That belongs to Yulin.

454
00:32:16,250 --> 00:32:17,330
Don't give it to him.

455
00:32:19,980 --> 00:32:21,050
Take Mr. Zhou away.

456
00:32:21,719 --> 00:32:23,252
We'll meet at the foot of the mountain.

457
00:32:24,140 --> 00:32:25,140
I'll wait there for you.

458
00:32:39,570 --> 00:32:40,490
Elder Tianji.

459
00:32:44,220 --> 00:32:45,290
Kid.

460
00:32:45,700 --> 00:32:47,260
(Duan Jiuxiu, Elder Tianji)
Sharp eyes.

461
00:32:47,290 --> 00:32:49,050
You recognized me.

462
00:32:51,410 --> 00:32:53,140
You were once Elder Tianji,

463
00:32:54,180 --> 00:32:55,810
but now you're reduced

464
00:32:56,700 --> 00:32:57,900
to following behind,

465
00:32:58,140 --> 00:32:59,090
acting as a servant.

466
00:32:59,490 --> 00:33:01,570
Truly tragic.

467
00:33:02,380 --> 00:33:03,860
You're asking for death.

468
00:33:08,090 --> 00:33:09,380
I heard that one is the weakest

469
00:33:09,380 --> 00:33:10,730
among Nie Hengcheng's

470
00:33:11,090 --> 00:33:12,490
four disciples.

471
00:33:13,530 --> 00:33:15,900
He survived only

472
00:33:16,810 --> 00:33:18,700
by flattering Nie Zhe daily.

473
00:33:19,770 --> 00:33:20,610
I think

474
00:33:21,140 --> 00:33:22,810
it must be you, Chen Shu.

475
00:33:22,810 --> 00:33:24,810
(Chen Shu, Li Sect)

476
00:33:24,810 --> 00:33:26,940
You know too much.

477
00:33:27,090 --> 00:33:28,810
I think you've grown tired of living.

478
00:33:28,810 --> 00:33:30,140
Who are you?

479
00:33:30,860 --> 00:33:31,700
Who am I?

480
00:33:32,050 --> 00:33:33,050
I'm your ancestor.

481
00:33:38,660 --> 00:33:39,620
Wudu Palm.

482
00:33:40,660 --> 00:33:42,180
You recognize it.

483
00:33:42,770 --> 00:33:44,700
You're of the Li Sect?

484
00:33:45,050 --> 00:33:46,220
As a Li Sect member,

485
00:33:47,280 --> 00:33:48,730
how dare you covet the Ziwei Method,

486
00:33:48,730 --> 00:33:49,620
wanting to practice it?

487
00:33:51,010 --> 00:33:52,620
If Nie Zhe knew,

488
00:33:53,250 --> 00:33:54,483
your bones would be gouged out,

489
00:33:54,770 --> 00:33:55,810
and you'd be beheaded.

490
00:33:56,220 --> 00:33:57,420
How arrogant

491
00:33:57,420 --> 00:33:58,900
before death.

492
00:34:15,260 --> 00:34:16,333
(His skills are so strong.)

493
00:34:16,530 --> 00:34:17,820
(He should be able to escape.)

494
00:34:19,130 --> 00:34:19,970
No.

495
00:34:20,980 --> 00:34:21,940
I must help him.

496
00:34:24,210 --> 00:34:25,050
Miss Feng.

497
00:34:26,010 --> 00:34:26,940
Miss Feng.

498
00:34:32,650 --> 00:34:33,490
Mr. Zhou,

499
00:34:33,820 --> 00:34:34,660
how are you?

500
00:34:38,740 --> 00:34:40,170
Thanks to your medicine,

501
00:34:40,740 --> 00:34:41,580
I'm much better.

502
00:34:41,860 --> 00:34:42,700
Thank you.

503
00:34:43,900 --> 00:34:45,130
Then rest a bit.

504
00:34:45,690 --> 00:34:47,260
We'll leave first.

505
00:34:47,780 --> 00:34:49,610
I, as a father, have failed.

506
00:34:50,300 --> 00:34:51,650
I can't take my son home

507
00:34:52,090 --> 00:34:53,490
and have to leave him alone

508
00:34:53,490 --> 00:34:55,210
in this snow-covered mountain.

509
00:34:57,170 --> 00:34:59,010
You must protect the saliva.

510
00:34:59,300 --> 00:35:02,980
It's my son's last item for me.

511
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:07,980
Mr. Zhou, young lady,

512
00:35:07,980 --> 00:35:08,820
you two are here.

513
00:35:08,980 --> 00:35:10,133
We've looked for a long time.

514
00:35:10,340 --> 00:35:11,180
Where are they?

515
00:35:14,380 --> 00:35:15,420
Your lover

516
00:35:15,780 --> 00:35:16,620
stubbornly refused

517
00:35:16,860 --> 00:35:17,700
to leave

518
00:35:18,420 --> 00:35:19,420
and was swallowed

519
00:35:20,130 --> 00:35:21,010
by the python

520
00:35:22,780 --> 00:35:23,900
with Jiu.

521
00:35:31,740 --> 00:35:32,650
He's dead?

522
00:35:33,780 --> 00:35:35,210
The python was too fierce.

523
00:35:35,530 --> 00:35:37,460
Its icy breath killed him instantly.

524
00:35:38,090 --> 00:35:40,050
What a pity for the cute young man.

525
00:35:40,820 --> 00:35:41,780
My condolences.

526
00:35:48,610 --> 00:35:49,450
Young lady,

527
00:35:50,690 --> 00:35:52,090
you still have the saliva, right?

528
00:35:52,650 --> 00:35:54,170
Jiu was wrong to take it,

529
00:35:54,460 --> 00:35:56,380
but this saliva is vital to our master.

530
00:35:56,650 --> 00:35:58,460
Now, it's useless for you.

531
00:35:58,820 --> 00:35:59,753
Why not sell it to us?

532
00:36:00,260 --> 00:36:01,100
Set a price.

533
00:36:01,900 --> 00:36:02,740
A thousand gold?

534
00:36:02,940 --> 00:36:04,430
Miss Feng, don't listen to them.

535
00:36:04,460 --> 00:36:05,300
They are bad people.

536
00:36:05,820 --> 00:36:06,940
Once we restrain them,

537
00:36:07,490 --> 00:36:08,636
we'll go find your companion.

538
00:36:30,010 --> 00:36:30,940
Sunshine Blade...

539
00:36:33,650 --> 00:36:34,530
You are Cai Zhao?

540
00:36:35,090 --> 00:36:35,930
Uncle Zhou,

541
00:36:36,740 --> 00:36:37,650
long time no see

542
00:36:37,980 --> 00:36:39,010
since childhood.

543
00:36:39,380 --> 00:36:40,780
How have you been?

544
00:36:41,300 --> 00:36:42,210
Kid,

545
00:36:42,570 --> 00:36:44,050
why attack me?

546
00:36:44,490 --> 00:36:46,260
My aunt grew up in Peiqiong Manor

547
00:36:46,570 --> 00:36:47,410
and could recognize

548
00:36:47,780 --> 00:36:49,213
the Zhous' swordsmanship blindfolded.

549
00:36:49,940 --> 00:36:51,090
I don't have eyes on my back,

550
00:36:51,740 --> 00:36:53,130
but I saw your shadow.

551
00:36:54,090 --> 00:36:55,300
Your sword

552
00:36:55,820 --> 00:36:57,780
is in the Moonlight Drinking stance,

553
00:36:58,490 --> 00:37:00,530
a close combat technique.

554
00:37:01,690 --> 00:37:03,260
They were so far apart.

555
00:37:03,940 --> 00:37:04,780
Uncle Zhou,

556
00:37:05,740 --> 00:37:07,490
who exactly are you trying to kill?

557
00:37:08,340 --> 00:37:09,210
Actually, I...

558
00:37:09,210 --> 00:37:10,170
I felt it was strange

559
00:37:10,860 --> 00:37:11,980
in the ice cave.

560
00:37:12,260 --> 00:37:13,460
Seeing the corpse of your kin,

561
00:37:13,780 --> 00:37:14,980
you kept digging in his hands.

562
00:37:19,300 --> 00:37:20,170
You didn't come

563
00:37:20,860 --> 00:37:23,010
for your son

564
00:37:24,010 --> 00:37:25,570
but for the saliva.

565
00:37:26,420 --> 00:37:27,690
That is Yulin's item.

566
00:37:27,860 --> 00:37:29,740
Zhao, if I wanted to harm you,

567
00:37:30,050 --> 00:37:32,090
why did I risk my life to protect you?

568
00:37:32,090 --> 00:37:33,490
That was the reason

569
00:37:34,340 --> 00:37:35,650
that I dismissed my doubts.

570
00:37:36,420 --> 00:37:37,780
That's why I healed you.

571
00:37:37,940 --> 00:37:38,860
Now, I see.

572
00:37:39,170 --> 00:37:40,940
It was just a ruse.

573
00:37:41,570 --> 00:37:42,410
Zhao,

574
00:37:42,980 --> 00:37:44,340
we are both from the Six Sects.

575
00:37:44,340 --> 00:37:45,690
I was friends with your aunt.

576
00:37:45,720 --> 00:37:46,570
Why say this?

577
00:37:46,570 --> 00:37:47,860
That's exactly why

578
00:37:47,860 --> 00:37:49,300
I didn't want to believe it,

579
00:37:50,980 --> 00:37:52,130
but just now,

580
00:37:52,940 --> 00:37:54,340
I had no choice but to confirm.

581
00:37:55,610 --> 00:37:58,420
You schemed for the saliva.

582
00:37:58,860 --> 00:38:00,650
What exactly do you want with it?

583
00:38:04,193 --> 00:38:05,460
Young lady, what are you doing?

584
00:38:05,460 --> 00:38:06,940
I heard saliva melts in fire.

585
